 "remarks": "Gracious and light-filled, this stunning 5200 sq ft. classic, located on coveted Kimberly Place, offers the best of in-town living! This home has four fully finished floors, high ceilings, detailed millwork, hardwood floors, versatile floor plan, and lovely private rear yard with expansive terrace. This five bedroom, four full and one half bath home offers a gorgeous new custom-built kitchen with high end appliances, large island, and dining area that opens into a fabulous family room with fireplace and built-ins. The spacious, newly renovated lower level with full bath, has endless possibilities for play, exercise and work. Additional improvements include new cedar roof, copper gutters, complete painting of interior and exterior, new cedar fencing, and so much more. This desirable location offers a short walk to town and the New Canaan train station!",
